What lies on the path between Bluespace travel is the unknown in the world that "Just works" ? Eidolon Research Group posed this question to investors leading to the subsequent development of project "Black Labyrinth", a blanket name used to refer to any of the multitude of sub-projects under its umbrella.

Black Labyrinth is responsible for the creatin of the Echelon Voidwalker, an experimental protean unit modified for bluespace void transferrence & reconnaissance operations. These units would be sent via [REDACTED] through void space to gather data, in the early days of the project units would seldom return from the operation however this was not needed as all data would be submitted in real time do to the [REDACTED] tether. The ones that did happen to return were stricken with the named void entrophy or "Nanite Rot", this rot alters the exisiting protean nanites composition leading them to push out through the shell producing a violet hue on contact outside of its host. It is to note that this affect was only found to populate on the synth-flesh weaves between their protective plates, the shell itself reamains undamaged. This void flesh was then harvested for the application of Oblivion Therapy, a treatment process used for cognical modification. Oblivion Therapy was intended as an alternative to other psychological treatments, marketed as "Bluespace for your thoughts", a way to completely rewrite the mind & memory.
